{"tid":1168023,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[慎入] AOA不如爽性解散埋佢啦  AOA智珉爆瘦疑似厭食症！","createTime":"2019-05-23T11:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T18:13:23.000Z","uid":74065,"like":9,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3af7f5cb5637acd16e8249bb499f19289671e8fd","tid":1168023,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T11:53:16.000Z","msg":"南韓女團AOA成員智珉雖然個子嬌小，但原本身材凹凸有致，有著健康活力美感，但近來被發現她突然爆瘦，四肢瘦成皮包骨，臉型也變得細長，過於纖細的體態被懷疑是否得了厭食症，在網路掀起討論。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4114/d4114753.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4114%2Fd4114753.jpg&h=9497409d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲AOA智珉爆瘦，被網友猜測是否得了厭食症。（圖／翻攝自智珉IG）<br />\n<br />\n智珉在最近更新的照片中，穿著牛仔褲與露肚上衣，開心對鏡頭露齒大笑，似乎沒有被外界對她身材的輿論給影響，不過對比過往照片，她的確瘦到一個不像話。<br />\n<br />\n在近期幾張照片，她吃著冰淇淋坐在英國街頭，臉頰明顯凹陷沒肉，引起粉絲擔心「健康不會是出問題了吧？」，連知名女主持人宋恩伊（송은이）都在底下留言：「很辛苦嗎？」為她感到擔心，網路也開始傳出智珉罹患厭食症的可能性。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4114/d4114754.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4114%2Fd4114754.jpg&h=9e524984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲宋恩伊也來關心：你很辛苦吧？。（圖／翻攝自智珉IG）<br />\n<br />\n就有網友留言表示，「真的看起來非常像厭食症患者啊，越來越乾瘦了。」也有人留言，「厭食症的人常常不覺得自己已經不健康了」、「看上去真的很像生病」，不過對此智珉的經紀公司FNC娛樂否認謠言，並傳達「沒有任何健康上的異常」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3893/d3893136.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3893%2Fd3893136.jpg&h=67d86d68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼智珉最近過瘦的樣子引起討論。（圖／翻攝自智珉IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3893/d3893137.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3893%2Fd3893137.jpg&h=ab726df6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而AOA目前又有一名成員珉娥確定退團，其餘5人包含智珉、酉奈、惠晶、雪炫與澯美都完成了續約，但短期內將會以個人活動為主，公司尚未公布有任何團體回歸的計畫。<br />\n<br />\nCHOA又一早走左<br />\nMINA一完約DEL晒IG野走埋<br />\n再加多個皮包骨<br />\n搵鬼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f0a0273d38dd92aac375f0d0c6d454d9946666","tid":1168023,"uid":46435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T11:57:36.000Z","msg":"wa diu 似道友多d.."},{"pid":"e7341400e6dd58216646761f1b3a25f796068518","tid":1168023,"uid":3405,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T11:58:53.000Z","msg":"AOA執柒左佢啦<br />\nJIMIN自從CHOA走左之後變晒<br />\n不如一齊走好過"},{"pid":"3d21ad8d5c11d3d2cfe2e8017148e34515329f4b","tid":1168023,"uid":64476,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T11:59:36.000Z","msg":"以前覺得佢好正 貓女個期"},{"pid":"651647287bdd2ccb75f426a93793cfdfad4dfde7","tid":1168023,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3f0a0273d38dd92aac375f0d0c6d454d9946666","tid":1168023,"uid":46435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T11:57:36.000Z","msg":"wa diu 似道友多d.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T12:00:34.000Z","msg":"輕到可以單手托起黎砌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1493b46bfac815712641e68da045bb73260f1d6","tid":1168023,"uid":223790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T12:01:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"13fab4b6bc652967f1eebd6e05d0cbe2b234bfeb","tid":1168023,"uid":223790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T12:01:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a0714beb7120eb4ae5afab25a44dbe0331c06ed","tid":1168023,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7341400e6dd58216646761f1b3a25f796068518","tid":1168023,"uid":3405,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T11:58:53.000Z","msg":"AOA執柒左佢啦<br />\nJIMIN自從CHOA走左之後變晒<br />\n不如一齊走好過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T12:01:54.000Z","msg":"CHOA走個陣JIMIN IG好似有PO話咩<br />\n咁相信你但卻比你背叛 大約咁既野"},{"pid":"15a0b2de3d5ed96c8c7c81b4cfa40b4bc75ba648","tid":1168023,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sc